casebody.data:
Crosby et al., Appellants, v. Delaware & H. Canal Co., Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 21, 1889.)

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Putnam, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. Case certified to court of appeals. For former report, see 5 N. Y. Supp. 949.
